            <p>
                We are extremely devoted to Gary, either on personal or musical standpoints. He was able to

                merge his soul in his music, and this can be clearly felt note by note, sometimes touching very

                sensitive topics in his lyrics. He is/was a truly inspiring musician and our tribute to him is what

                we really want to remember of him : on the stage, playing loud with the band, transmitting

                emotions to the people. His music will be in our hearts forever.  Luca, Dario, Willy and Marco –

                Back To Front
